summary: This one takes some explanation, since it’s from as-yet unpublished AU story: So, in I Shall Save Myself, Senya becomes Empress...
body:
This one takes some explanation, since it’s from as-yet unpublished AU story:

So, in I Shall Save Myself, Senya becomes Empress of Zakuul. At one point in the future, she is confronted in her throne room, surrounded by her Knights, by one who would take the Throne. He calls on her to face him as the Empress. She sicks the Knights on him, and when he objects, she responds, “You wished me to fight as an Empress, and so I am.”

Still with me?

Now, Incorrect I Shall Save Myself Quotes

Villain: Fight me as the Empress! Prove to me that you can…

(gets clobbered by the Knights)

Empress Senya: I have nothing to prove to you.

blog.name: minerfromtarn
blog.title: Towards Peace
blog.description:
"Be he foe or friend, be he foul or clean,

brood of Morgoth or bright Vala,

Elda or Maia or Aftercomer,

Man yet unborn upon Middle-earth,

neither law, nor love, nor league of swords,

dread nor danger, not Doom itself,

shall defend him from Fëanor, and Fëanor's kin,

whoso hideth or hoardeth, or in hand taketh,

finding keepeth or afar casteth

a Silmaril. This swear we all:

death we will deal him ere Day's ending,

woe unto world's end! Our word hear thou,

Eru Allfather! To the everlasting

Darkness doom us if our deed faileth.

On the holy mountain hear in witness

and our vow remember, Manwë and Varda!"

Bi/nonbinary, any pronoun works, Decepticon, Jew

blog.name: sunshineoptimismandangels
blog.title: Be Generous. Be Grateful. Work hard.
blog.description:
Hi I’m Meag! (short for Meagan – it is just spelled awkwardly). Her/She. I love Glee, Good Omens, Doctor Who, Critical Role, and a whole slew of other things that I post randomly. I try to tag all shows that aren’t Glee since this started out as mainly a Glee/Klaine blog. I also write some Klaine fanfiction, you can find me on FF.net and AO3 (most updated fics on AO3). Someday I’ll get an updated fic page here on Tumblr... someday. I’m very open to prompts if you have them, but I can’t promise I’ll write it. Lastly, I LOVE my fandom family and my ask box is always open so feel free to say hello! 
*Header art used by permission from the very talented Giulia Hrvatin (mascaratear on Tumblr)
